Package: rmaverick
Type: Package
Title: Analysis of population structure
Version: 1.0.6
Date: 2018-04-06
URL: https://bobverity.github.io/rmaverick/
Authors@R: as.person("Bob Verity <r.verity@imperial.ac.uk> [aut, cre]")
Maintainer: Robert Verity <r.verity@imperial.ac.uk>
Description: Carries out analysis of genetic population structure using a
    mixture model analogous to STRUCTURE and related methods. Uses thermodynamic
    integration to estimate the evidence for each number of subpopulations and to
    compare between different evolutionary models.
License: MIT + file LICENSE
BugReports: https://github.com/bobverity/rmaverick/issues
Imports:
    Rcpp (>= 0.12.14),
    parallel,
    coda,
    ggplot2,
    gridExtra,
    dplyr
LinkingTo:
    Rcpp
RoxygenNote: 7.1.1
Suggests: 
    testthat,
    knitr,
    rmarkdown
SystemRequirements:
    C++11
VignetteBuilder: knitr
Encoding: UTF-8
